<i>noun</i>: 무서움 [무서움], 두려움 [두려움], 공포심 [공ː포심], 공포감 [공ː포감], 공포 [공ː포], 겁대가리 [겁때가리], 겁 [겁] <i>verb</i>: 우려하다 [우려하다], 우려되다 [우려되다/우려뒈다], 두려워하다 [두려워하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>무서움 [무서움]</dt><br>
<dd>fear; terror</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상이 꺼려지거나 무슨 일이 일어날까 겁나는 마음. 또는 그런 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of being scared of an object or that something will happen, or such a feeling.</dd><br>
<dt>두려움 [두려움]</dt><br>
<dd>fear</dd><br>
<dd>겁나고 꺼려지는 마음. 또는 그런 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of fear and concern, or such a feeling.</dd><br>
<dt>공포심 [공ː포심]</dt><br>
<dd>fear</dd><br>
<dd>두렵고 무서운 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The mood of being scared and afraid.</dd><br>
<dt>공포감 [공ː포감]</dt><br>
<dd>fear</dd><br>
<dd>무섭고 두려운 느낌이나 기분.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling or mood of being scared and afraid.</dd><br>
<dt>공포 [공ː포]</dt><br>
<dd>fear</dd><br>
<dd>두렵고 무서움.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being scared and afraid.</dd><br>
<dt>겁대가리 [겁때가리]</dt><br>
<dd>chicken-heartedness; fear</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 무서워하는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) A fearful mind.</dd><br>
<dt>겁 [겁]</dt><br>
<dd>fear; fright</dd><br>
<dd>무서워서 불안해하는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of mind when one is scared or anxious.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>우려하다 [우려하다]</dt><br>
<dd>be concerned; fear</dd><br>
<dd>근심하거나 걱정하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To worry or feel anxious.</dd><br>
<dt>우려되다 [우려되다/우려뒈다]</dt><br>
<dd>fear; be concerned</dd><br>
<dd>근심되거나 걱정되다.</dd><br>
<dd>To worry or feel anxious.</dd><br>
<dt>두려워하다 [두려워하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. fear; dread; be afraid; be terrified</dd><br>
<dd>무섭고 겁이나 몹시 피하고 싶어 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To want to avoid something or someone as one feels scared or fearful.</dd><br>
<dd>2. be worried; be nervous; mind</dd><br>
<dd>걱정하고 불안해하거나 꺼리다.</dd><br>
<dd>To be worried, insecure, or reluctant.</dd><br>
<dd>3. be reluctant to meet</dd><br>
<dd>상대방을 대하기 어려워하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To feel difficult or reluctant to meet another person.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>